cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a deep learning model for typographic analysis, which involves analyzing the structure and style of fonts. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including computer vision (cs.CV) for image analysis, machine learning (cs.LG) for the deep learning model, artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for the generative model, graphics (cs.GR) for the typography analysis, and computational linguistics (cs.CL) for the character-specific content embeddings.
